datavisualizer.views

Class TraceInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • datavisualizer.views.TraceInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<TraceInfo>

    public class TraceInfo
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<TraceInfo>
    This class represents a trace in the xyGraph. It stores all info about a task and a list of StateInfo identifying each point in the plot (time, state). Objects of this class are comparable; provide an intrinsic ordering primarily by core and secondarily by priority.
    Author:
    Samy Dafir, Sophie Reischl, Dominik Baumgartner
